<br>
Lootz division is one roll per toon level based everyone rolls on every item of value.<br>
<br>
<br>
65 Ran 600-1000<br>
64 Ran 500-1000<br>
63 Ran 400-1000<br>
62 Ran 300-1000<br>
61 Ran 200-1000<br>
60 Ran 100-1000<br>
59 Ran 1-1000<br>
<br>
Everyone rolls on all items of value (junks item worth under 100pp goes to clerics in exchange for virtue for everyone in raid), no consideration if you can equip it or not. If you win an item you cannot equip raid will wait until the item rots (and buff whatever in meantime), you can trade the looting rights for pp or for other items or for someones subsequent rolls. Once you win its your property 100percent you do whatever you want with it, if its gonna rot in one minute then sell it for 100pp if you want, its all on you once you win.<br>
<br>
I.E. you are a Cleric you win a Warrior only item. You say to Warrior in the raid, I'll let you loot this in exchange for your rolls on the next 4 items..... If the warrior leaves before we kill the next 4 items you are out. You have to be present from when we engage the mob to when we kill it to roll. If you die you still roll. We won't roll until all is rezed. <br>
